"name": "醉酒的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "芙蓉", "content": " 人群......"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "芙蓉", "content": "這麼快就散了？"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊，你怎麼樣？沒受傷吧！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒事，可是琴......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，這大提琴......面板破得這麼嚴重，還能修嗎？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝你出手相助。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不客氣。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初次見面——應該不是初次見面了吧。不過，我們一直沒能好好打個招呼。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，剛才還挺危險的。雖然夕照區也是維謝海姆的一部分，但一般的治安官可不想來這。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果他們真的動了手，短時間內未必會有人來幫你。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再次向你表示感謝。我該怎麼稱呼你？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直接叫我黑鍵就好。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，黑鍵，他們說的預言，你聽說過嗎？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完全沒有。我也是剛剛從人群口中聽見這個詞的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，這個預言完全沒有傳到高庭區，是嗎......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高庭區？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維謝海姆的貴族應該都住在高庭區，不是嗎？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別把我和他們相提並論。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？你不是維謝海姆的......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的確不是維謝海姆本地人。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，隨意推測一位貴族的身份可不是什麼禮貌的舉動。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你是專程來夕照區參加車爾尼先生的音樂會的？你也是感染者？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，我並未感染礦石病。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我聽別人說，來這參加音樂會的都是感染者——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對話就到此為止吧。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很著急？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然著急。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和白堊本來想去車爾尼先生家，請他驗收我們今天練琴的成果，結果遇到了這檔事。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，耽誤了你的時間。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先回辦事處了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，別傷心了，先去車爾尼家吧。他那麼喜歡你，會給你重新挑一把琴的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$2"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我不是那個意思......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒事。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過也真奇怪，我完全沒聽過什麼“陛下的預言”啊。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（難道是格特魯德？）", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒是隱隱約約聽過一些......但是很模糊，也沒提什麼薩卡茲......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，算了，音樂會要緊。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這群人也真是，要是真喜歡，就應該去女皇之聲面前一口一個“那位陛下”“那位陛下”，那才好玩呢。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不說這些了，我們趕緊去車爾尼家吧。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，琴......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是說過了嗎，車爾尼會給你挑一把的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，這也不是你的錯，就算車爾尼要跟你計較這把琴，也還有我呢。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$2"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#10$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g5_czernyhome", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "琴壞了？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#4$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你們也去打架鬥毆了？！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是這樣的——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊，你說。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來的路上，我和黑鍵遇到了芙蓉。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芙蓉？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她被一幫人圍攻了，那些人說她是魔族，會給夕照區帶來災難。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無稽之談。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想去保護芙蓉，結果......大提琴被法術打壞了。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在街上放法術，這群人腦子到底出了什麼毛病！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後你打退了他們？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是黑鍵用法術驅散了人群，幫我和芙蓉解了圍。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#10$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他？幫你解圍？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#10$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行，我知道了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這把壞琴......唉，像樣的大提琴，我也只有這一把啊。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別道歉了，這不是你的錯，反而是我，應該代表夕照區，替那些蠢貨給你道歉。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之你先把琴放這吧，我再找找看，有沒有別的琴給你用。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就剩這把量產貨了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先湊合一下，我來驗收你們練習的成果。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開始吧！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車爾尼先生，您......意下如何？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進步不是沒有。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且對你們來說，這是首只練了一天的新曲子，我也不應該要求太多。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但之前的問題，幾乎一個也沒解決。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾乎一個也沒解決？怎麼——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵反應的速度快了不少，可還是會在自己的段落忘乎所以，好像在炫耀什麼一樣，最後還是要白堊來遷就你。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連曲子都還沒完全熟悉，有什麼好炫耀的？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那些裝飾音，倒是都吹出來了，可是連氣息都快不穩了，有意義嗎？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊呢，還是比較扎實的，主要的問題也是熟練度，再練練應該會好很多。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但《晨暮》再怎麼說也是二重奏，不可能讓一方一直遷就另一方。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我真的想撤掉《晨暮》了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車爾尼先生......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直接說。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可不可以這樣，讓黑鍵配合您的鋼琴伴奏再試一次？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可不會像你一樣遷就他，他出醜可不要怪我。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": 