 "attributes": {"content": "我完全沒打算配合你的節奏，你自己的部分還是比較穩定地完成了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看出來了，白堊確實是在遷就你，但他只是在遷就你的習慣，不是在遷就你的水準。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有待提高的地方還有一大堆，但最低標準，你算是摸到了邊。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說......？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通過。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了！", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#12$2"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（長出一口氣）", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#12$2"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醜話說在前頭，我今天的標準已經拉到最低了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會隨時找你們驗收成果，如果在演出前還是只有這種水準的話，我一樣不讓你們上台，明白了嗎？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#10$1"}}, {"i